OL,5, Separating parents in England and Wales
OL,6, could face fines for refusing to try   
OL,7, mediation under new proposals.         
OL,9,FThe government is set to make sessions 
OL,10,Fmandatory and offer funding support in 
OL,11,Fan effort to divert cases away from    
OL,12,Funder-pressure family courts.          
OL,14,FJustice Secretary Dominic Raab said    
OL,15,F"lengthy and combative courtroom       
OL,16,Fbattles" were harmful for children.    
OL,18,FBut the Law Society said the plan could
OL,19,Fput victims of undetected coercive     
OL,20,Fcontrol in a vulnerable position.      
